# chktex configuration for TAOCP solutions
# Suppress warnings that are false positives for math-heavy LaTeX documents

# Warning 2: Non-breaking space before references
# Warning 3: Enclose previous parenthesis with {} — false positive in math
# Warning 8: Wrong dash length — false positive in titles like 1.2.1-10
# Warning 9: ) expected — false positive in math mode
# Warning 10: Solo ) found — false positive in math mode
# Warning 12: Interword spacing — stylistic preference
# Warning 13: Intersentence spacing — stylistic preference
# Warning 15: No match for ( — false positive in math mode
# Warning 16: Mathmode still on — false positive due to template not resolved
# Warning 17: Mismatched parentheses count — false positive in multi-line math
# Warning 25: Put subscript between {} — stylistic, F_n is fine
# Warning 27: Could not execute LaTeX command — template path not resolved
# Warning 35: Use \gcd/\min/\max — false positives for variable names
# Warning 36: Space before parenthesis — false positive in math mode

CmdLine
{
    -n2 -n3 -n8 -n9 -n10 -n12 -n13 -n15 -n16 -n17 -n25 -n27 -n35 -n36
}
